							<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/invalid-backup-file/" target="_blank">Detail teknis</a>','The archive file appears to be corrupted. Follow <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/corrupted-archive/" target="_blank">this article</a> for possible fixes.'=>'File arsip rusak. Ikuti panduan di <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/corrupted-archive/" target="_blank">artikel ini</a> untuk menyelesaikan masalah.','Your backup is from a PHP %1$s but the site that you are importing to is PHP %2$s. This could cause the import to fail. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/migrate-wordpress-from-php-5-to-php-7/" target="_blank">Technical details</a>'=>'Cadangan Anda adalah dari PHP %1$s tetapi situs yang Anda impor adalah PHP %2$s. Hal ini dapat menyebabkan gagal impor. <a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/migrate-wordpress-from-php-5-to-php-7/" target="_blank">Detail teknis</a>','Drag & Drop a backup to import it'=>'Drag & Drop cadangan untuk mengimpor','Exporting database...<br />%1$d%% complete<br />%2$s records saved'=>'Mengekspor database... <br />%1$d%% lengkap<br />%2$s record disimpan','Backup restore requires the Unlimited Extension. <a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">Get it here</a>'=>'Pemulihan cadangan juga tersedia melalui ekstensi Unlimited. <a href="https://servmask.com/products/unlimited-extension" target="_blank">Dapatkan di sini</a>','All-in-One WP Migration Command'=>'Semua-dalam-satu WP migrasi perintah','Preparing to export...'=>'Bersiap-siap untuk ekspor...','%s ago'=>'%s yang lalu','Your purchase ID is invalid. Please <a href="mailto:support@servmask.com">contact us</a>.'=>'ID pembelian Anda tidak valid, silahkan <a href="mailto:support@servmask.com">hubungi kami</a>.','Are you sure you want to delete this backup?'=>'Anda yakin ingin menghapus cadangan ini?','Please do not close this browser window or your import will fail'=>'Jangan tutup jendela browser ini atau Anda impor akan gagal','Continue'=>'Lanjutkan','Proceed'=>'Lanjutkan','Stop import'=>'Menghentikan impor','Stop export'=>'Berhenti ekspor','Close'=>'Tutup','Preparing configuration...'=>'Mempersiapkan konfigurasi...','Archiving configuration...<br />%d%% complete'=>'Pengarsipan konfigurasi... <br />%d%% selesai','Unpacking archive...<br />%d%% complete'=>'Membongkar Arsip...<br />%d%% lengkap','Archiving database...<br />%d%% complete'=>'Pengarsipan database...<br />%d%% lengkap','Restoring database...<br />%d%% complete'=>'Memulihkan database... <br />%d%% lengkap','Preparing to import...'=>'Mempersiapkan untuk mengimpor...','Monthly'=>'Bulanan','Weekly'=>'Mingguan','Activating mu-plugins...'=>'Mengaktifkan mu-plugins...','Do <strong>not</strong> replace email domain'=>'<strong>Jangan</strong> gantikan domain email','Preparing blogs...'=>'Mempersiapkan blogs...','Check for updates'=>'Cek Pembaruan','ServMask'=>'ServMask','https://servmask.com/'=>'https://servmask.com/','Import Site'=>'Impor situs','Import From'=>'Impor dari','Export Site'=>'Ekspor situs','Once the file is successfully downloaded on your computer, you can import it to any of your WordPress sites.'=>'Setelah file tersebut berhasil di-download pada komputer Anda, Anda dapat mengimpor ke salah satu situs WordPress Anda.','Press "Export" button and the site archive file will pop up in your browser.'=>'Tekan tombol "Ekspor" dan file arsip situs akan muncul di peramban.','In the advanced settings section you can configure more precisely the way of exporting.'=>'Di bagian pengaturan lanjutan Anda dapat mengkonfigurasi lebih tepatnya cara mengekspor.','Add'=>'Menambahkan','in the database'=>'dalam database','<another-text>'=>'<another-text>','Replace with'=>'Ganti dengan','<text>'=>'<text>','File'=>'Berkas','(click to expand)'=>'(Klik untuk membuka pengaturan kolom)','Advanced options'=>'Pengaturan Tingkat Lanjut','Tweet'=>'Mengirimkan tweet','Cancel'=>'Batalkan','Send'=>'Kirim','Enter a pas